=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">here is a claim</a> that the people buying high-strike AMC cal=
l options are actually doing it because they are selling call spreads, as a=
 relatively sane way to bet against the stock.=C2=A0</p>
